(ns helins.binf.test

  "Testing core view utilities.
  
   R/W tests ensures a few things at once such as:

   - Endianess is randomized
   - Positioning behaves well both in absolute and relative R/W
   - Operating consistenly on subviews"

  {:author "Adam Helins"}

